{"tid":1994934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】打壓新疆「幫凶」 亞馬遜、IBM等向黑名單公司採購鏡頭","createTime":"2020-04-29T23:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T03:50:37.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b03792f9dc15a1cae73ea811662b6bf667056479","tid":1994934,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T23:46:46.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）美國體溫探測器材短缺，網上零售巨頭亞馬遜、電腦公司國際商業機器（IBM）及汽車生產商佳士拿（Chrysler），被揭向遭美國政府列入黑名單的中國公司浙江大華科技，採購體溫探測鏡頭。亞馬遜訂單最多，總額達1,000萬元（美元，下同），共買入1,500組鏡頭。三間公司均未有承認是否有向浙江大華採購。<br />\n<br />\n全文請看蘋果：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200430&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60887779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200430%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60887779&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=60b43b78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200430%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60887779&h=460ae07d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200430&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60887779</a>"},{"pid":"f7a8471010065be594e4f4ef631a676a8ab0559a","tid":1994934,"uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T23:49:03.000Z","msg":"香港有間公司叫樂信<br />\n地產商從樂信中購買生產大量鏡頭監控異見者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通過出賣平民討好警頭"},{"pid":"d798bddade9612271f0b6e705579fbc7fd561576","tid":1994934,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7a8471010065be594e4f4ef631a676a8ab0559a","tid":1994934,"uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T23:49:03.000Z","msg":"香港有間公司叫樂信<br />\n地產商從樂信中購買生產大量鏡頭監控異見者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通過出賣平民討好警頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T23:51:00.000Z","msg":"樂信咪即係樂聲香港代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107b6d248c6e95abff39f06241a80650b0e0cc1d","tid":1994934,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7a847